maybe Search is having an issue here.

33
00:02:03.810 --> 00:02:07.500
I can already rest assured that ShowCard
isn't causing any issues because ShowCard

34
00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:10.150
has no way to meddle with Search, right?

35
00:02:11.220 --> 00:02:14.970
That's the power of one-way data flow.

36
00:02:14.970 --> 00:02:19.394
So this is a powerful thing that I
think Facebook does really well,

37
00:02:19.394 --> 00:02:23.423
in particular with React and
some of their other libraries,

38
00:02:23.423 --> 00:02:27.782
is they really optimize for
debug ability and maintainability.

39
00:02:27.782 --> 00:02:33.198
And so this idea that you can see
a problem and eliminate entire

40
00:02:33.198 --> 00:02:39.672
swaths of your code where that problem
could not be, is really powerful.

41
00:02:39.672 --> 00:02:44.021
Cuz you can start having an issue, and you
just get to eliminate two-thirds of your

42
00:02:44.021 --> 00:02:48.390
